999029835115753480.text: Bowie was a creator who never was content to rest on his laurels. Even at the height of success, he was continually reinventing himself - working to push his creative and intellectual capacity.

999029689615355909.text: In 1997 he arranged a live stream of his concerts online and then launched his own ISP - Bowienet - in 1998. He even allowed fans to have their own email address on the domainhttps://www.theguardian.com/technology/2016/jan/11/david-bowie-bowienet-isp-internet …

999029604764528641.text: Always at the cutting edge of tech, Bowie designed his own app - the verbasizer - in 1995 to help him create lyrics and think laterally.https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x3IKLMgFaDA …

999029553434591232.text: Bowie was a lateral thinker, using tools like Oblique Strategies to push himself in new directions and connect disparate ideas.

999029508039675906.text: Bowie was a prolific creator and a deep thinker. He studied intently and let whatever he was fascinated by - Japanese Culture, Space, America - influence his performances in real time.

999029454272958464.text: But was Bowie actually gay? A few years after that daring statement he was quoted in playboy, "It's true -- I am a bisexual. But I can't deny that I've used that fact very well."

999029398702559233.text: Bowie wasn't afraid to use his sexuality to spur publicity. His style was androgynous and provocative. And a few years after homosexuality was decriminalized in the UK he declared "I’m gay. And always have been, even when I was David Jones."

999029289617100801.text: He was also a master at positioning and spin. At the age of 17 David started the "Society for the Prevention of Cruelty to Long-Haired Men" and made national news in the UKhttp://www.bbc.com/news/av/entertainment-arts-35278853/david-bowie-defends-long-hair-in-1964-tv-interview …

999029231408599040.text: Bowie was a performer in the days before large scale production crews. Initially he took on all of his own set and costume design and created a spectacle that combined the best of all these crafts
